  <summary>6/6/2002--Introduced.
Foreign Aid Impact Assessment Act - Directs the President to report periodically to Congress an analysis, on a country-by-country basis, of the impact and effectiveness of U.S. economic assistance provided to such country during the preceding three fiscal years.</summary>
